{
    "poem_title": "- 37 - A Juliana y Juana ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Lope de Vega",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Amanecieron en el claro oriente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "entre el aurora, perlas y cristales,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "los dos hermosos soles celestiales",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "que al mundo alumbra con su luz ardiente.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Amanecieron en el claro oriente,\nentre el aurora, perlas y cristales,\nlos dos hermosos soles celestiales\nque al mundo alumbra con su luz ardiente."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Daba el menor divino, refulgente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "con rayos de oro, luz a los mortales;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "daba el mayor los rayos orientales,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "cubiertos de una nube transparente.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Daba el menor divino, refulgente,\ncon rayos de oro, luz a los mortales;\ndaba el mayor los rayos orientales,\ncubiertos de una nube transparente."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Cual águila caudal miré atrevido",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "los bellos ojos de Juliana y Juana",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "contra los rayos del inmenso fuego...",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cual águila caudal miré atrevido\nlos bellos ojos de Juliana y Juana\ncontra los rayos del inmenso fuego..."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Mirelos solos de su luz movido,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "y por pagar mi confianza vana,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "hiriome el resplandor y quedé ciego.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+--++-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mirelos solos de su luz movido,\ny por pagar mi confianza vana,\nhiriome el resplandor y quedé ciego."
        }
    ]
}